msgid "# triton.language.static_range"
msgstr "# triton.language.static_range"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:4
msgid "`static_range` 是一个静态范围的迭代器，与 `range` 类似但会在编译时进行积极的循环展开优化。"
msgstr "`static_range` is a static range iterator, similar to `range` but performs aggressive loop unrolling optimization at compile time."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.static_range(arg1, arg2=None, step=None, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `constexpr` | 必需 | 起始值（单参数时作为结束值，从0开始） |\n"
"| `arg2` | `constexpr` | - | 结束值（不包含在范围内） |\n"
"| `step` | `constexpr` | `1` | 每次迭代的步长增量 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default Value | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------------|-------------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `constexpr` | Required | Start value (when used as a single parameter, it serves as the end value, starting from 0) |\n"
"| `arg2` | `constexpr` | - | End value (not included in the range) |\n"
"| `step` | `constexpr` | `1` | Step increment for each iteration |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not currently supported |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:14
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

