#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:20
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:22
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:24
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:26
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:28
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def optimized_kernel(x_ptr, y_ptr, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 使用static_range进行小规模循环展开，消除循环开销\n"
"    for i in tl.static_range(BLOCK_SIZE):\n"
"        # 当BLOCK_SIZE是编译时常量时，整个循环会被展开\n"
"        x = tl.load(x_ptr + i)\n"
"        y = x * x\n"
"        tl.store(y_ptr + i, y)\n"
"\n"
"    # 对比：使用range会有循环控制开销\n"
"    for i in tl.range(BLOCK_SIZE):\n"
"        # 这个循环在运行时会有循环控制逻辑\n"
"        x = tl.load(x_ptr + i)\n"
"        y = x * x\n"
"        tl.store(y_ptr + i, y)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/static_range.md:30
msgid "`static_range` 通过牺牲代码大小来换取运行时性能，适用于已知且较小的循环次数场景。"
msgstr "`static_range` trades off code size for runtime performance, making it suitable for scenarios with known and small loop iteration counts."

